      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -220,
        -120
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📋 Importação via Google Drive → Supabase\n\n**Antes de executar:**\n1. Edite o nó **\"Configurar Credenciais\"** com sua URL e service_role key do Supabase\n2. Conecte sua conta Google Drive nos nós de download\n3. Certifique-se que as tabelas `cadastros` e `pedidos` existem no Supabase com `id_cadastro` e `id_pagamento` como PRIMARY KEY\n\n**Arquivos configurados:**\n- cadastros → ID: 1JVTcdDrU1AEowE5P5iyx92NUJUCk4PwBBR1VrTyWeU0\n- pix_cartao → ID: 1-jM9AJLZfYF3FYyizHASKLZwIpJEgL5Bf3RHZPW-pBg\n- boletos → ID: 1I0TXMXe1u_lqrCiDyqLqp867RaU4fnMqtnXdRgs6UA8",
        "color": 3,
        "width": 520,
        "height": 360
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "911eac2f-9c7e-487a-bc0f-dbe794f9399c",
      "name": "Iniciar Importação",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "6ad65926-4adc-4c91-a57a-e9d1d38fb957",
      "name": "Configurar Credenciais",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        -220,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "manual",
        "includeOtherFields": false,
        "fields": {
          "values": [
            {
              "name": "supabaseUrl",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "string": "https://SEU_PROJETO.supabase.co"
            },
            {
              "name": "supabaseKey",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "string": "sua_service_role_key_aqui"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "executeOnce": true
    },
    {
